news.title: Holcim's spin-off Amrize targets robust growth through 2028 in USA
news.para: An Amrize listing by the end of the first half of 2025 remains on track, the company said in a statement ahead of its investor day in New York. Holcim targeted a $30 billion valuation when the spin-off was first announced in January 2024.

news.title: UK's warehouse REIT evaluates Blackstone's $633 million takeover proposal
news.para: The 115 pence-per-share proposal is a 4% increase from the previous one made jointly by Blackstone and global investment firm Sixth Street Partners.

news.title: UK: Bellway's profit rises 12% amid lower mortgage rates
news.para: Home sales in the UK got a boost in the first quarter as homebuyers tried to complete purchases before a property tax exemption expires from April 1 and by more UK rate cuts, although the pace of rate cuts is slow.

news.title: Citigroup leases 7.7 lakh sq ft office space in Pune's Kharadi for Rs 1,100 crore
news.para: The entire space is spread over 7th to 16th floor of Panchshil Business Hub and starting monthly rentals range between nearly Rs 2.02 crore to Rs 2.71 crore depending on the floor.

news.title: Maharashtra government to begin campaign from April 1 to update 7/12 land title records
news.para: ​​​"The campaign, referred to as the 'Live 7/12' initiative, involves updating inheritance records in land ownership documents, specifically for deceased landholders.

news.title: Illegal land allocations in Bikaner to be cancelled: Rajasthan Minister
news.para: "In accordance with the order issued on Feb 1, a committee under the chairmanship of the additional district collector (city) of Bikaner has been formed to examine these land allocation cases.

news.title: 315Work Avenue to invest around Rs 400 crore for expansion in 2025
news.para: Manas Mehrotra, founder, 315Work Avenue said, "The demand has gained greater traction with corporates and MNCs continuing to make a beeline to coworking spaces that have emerged as strong centres of growth."

news.title: Britain government to invest two billion pounds to build 18,000 affordable homes
news.para: Official figures, published on Monday, showed the average median house price cost 7.7 times the average full-time income in 2024. Temporary tax incentives for first-time buyers as well as for buyers of less expensive homes are due to expire at the end of this month.

news.title: Uttar Pradesh government approves second phase of YEIDA plan for 2031
news.para: Currently, all active development programs, land acquisition, and land allotment are taking place under Phase I of the Master Plan.

news.title: Indore: 10 industries receive land allotments in Pithampur sector 7
news.para: These ten industries have collectively proposed an investment of nearly Rs 3,000 crore and are expected to generate employment opportunities for approximately 6,000 people.

news.title: Kolkata: NKDA collects Rs 83 lakh from property tax and mutation fees
news.para: The outreach camps were held at different housing complexes like Sukhobristi Housing, Rosedale, Unitech, and a few others over a period of 14 days.

news.title: Home prices in Germany rise 1.9% in Q4 2024
news.para: Home prices began their decline in 2022 after the European Central Bank began a rapid increase in interest rates to curb rampant inflation, sparking Germany's worst real-estate crisis in decades.

news.title: Japan's Nomura Real Estate join hands with L&G to enter UK housing market
news.para: It's Nomura Real Estate's first foray into the UK rental home market, which has seen increasing foreign interest in recent years, with U.S. firms Blackstone and PGIM among those that have been pouring in cash.

news.title: Suryakumar & Devisha Yadav acquire two apartments in Mumbai for Rs 21.11 crore
news.para: The apartments have a total carpet area of 392.36 sq meters (4,222.76 sq ft) and a total built-up area of 424.46 sq meters (4,568 sq ft). The agreement also includes six designated car parking spaces.

news.title: Surat civic body removes 71 illegal structures in two years
news.para: These figures came up as part of a reply to Congress MLA from Vansda, Anant Patel, in the assembly. Patel asked for these details after he came to know about rampant illegal constructions in the city.

news.title: Indore leads the race with 478.3 million sq ft in green building footprints and urban infrastructure in MP
news.para: Sustainable projects have encompassed approximately 500.4 million sq ft of eco-friendly footprints in Madhya Pradesh, with 478.3 million sq ft exclusively in Indore.

news.title: Realtor and 10 others booked for Rs 7 crore property fraud in Ludhiana
news.para: Between April and September 2022, the company transferred Rs 7.61 crore to Mann's account, expecting the funds to be used for purchasing land from several individuals.

news.title: Andhra Pradesh government approves revised mobility plans in Vijayawada and Visakhapatnam
news.para: GO 215 authorises the consultant agency to prepare the revised CMP for Vijayawada Metro at a cost of 81.67 lakh, inclusive of 18% GST. Similarly, GO 216 grants permission to prepare the revised CMP for Visakhapatnam Metro at a cost of 84.47 lakh, inclusive of 18% GST.

news.title: Madras HC dismisses plea against Tidel park in Madurai
news.para: The court was hearing the petition filed by R Mayilsamy, Secretary of Neer Nilaigal Matrum Sutruchoozhal Paathukappu Nala Sangam-Madurai North.

news.title: About 25 illegal buildings on land notified for Noida airport razed in Jewar tehsil
news.para: Officials carried out a four-hour drive, targeting illegal houses and permanent structures on land notified for acquisition for the airport's third and fourth phases.
